headline.main: Belluno Defeats Favored Master Ace by Two and a Half Lengths; DASH VICTOR PAYS $30.90 AT BELMONT Belluno Takes Feature With Closing Rush -- Mielaison Beats Odds-on Bennet

results.snippet: Belluno, owned by Christopher Chenery and ridden by Eddie Arcaro, beat six others in the feature at Belmont Park yesterday. The performance was unexpected, for Belluno was next to the outsider in the wagering, and paid $30.90.
